在探討類木行星時，雖然「氣體」和「巨」兩詞經常合併使用，但以氫構成的氣體行星未必能演化到同[[太陽系|太陽系]]內類木行星的大小。比起質量較大或公轉半徑較大的行星，較靠近恆星的小氣體行星將因[[流體|流體]]逸散導致較快速的大氣成份流失。<ref>{{cite journal | id = {{citeseerx|10.1.1.122.9085}} | title = TRANSONIC HYDRODYNAMIC ESCAPE OF HYDROGEN FROM EXTRASOLAR PLANETARY ATMOSPHERES | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_astrophysical-journal_2005-03-10_621_2/page/1049 | author1 = Feng Tian | first2 = Owen B. | last2 = Toon | first3 = Alexander A. | last3 = Pavlov | first4 = H. | last4 = De Sterck | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 621 | pages = 1049–1060 |date=March 10, 2005 |bibcode = 2005ApJ...621.1049T |doi = 10.1086/427204 }}</ref><ref>[http://arxiv.org/pdf/1001.4851 Mass-radius relationships for exoplanets], Damian C. Swift, Jon Eggert, Damien G. Hicks, Sebastien Hamel, Kyle Caspersen, Eric Schwegler, and Gilbert W. Collins</ref>

